DAT
id=qid::label=str::text=lstr::
5536::$$$message_0049_0000_0000$$$::Soon after Fuji-nee leaves, I lock up and Sakura and I leave as well.::
5537::$$$message_0049_0001_0000$$$::"Senpai. I won't be able to come help out from tonight until Monday. Will that be all right?"[lr]::
5538::$$$message_0049_0001_0001$$$::"That's fine. Besides, it's the weekend. I bet you have friends to hang out with, so don't worry about me."::
5539::$$$message_0049_0002_0000$$$::"Eh... Oh, no that's not it! It really is for personal reasons, so I'm still going to practice at the club! S-so if you need anything just come to the dojo and I'll figure things out![lr]::
5540::$$$message_0049_0002_0001$$$::And I'm not going to go out just because it's the weekend. So...um...please don't get the wrong idea!" ::
5541::$$$message_0049_0003_0000$$$::"What?"[lr]::
5542::$$$message_0049_0003_0001$$$::Sakura's acting suspicious, or rather, she seems nervous.[lr]::
5543::$$$message_0049_0003_0002$$$::I don't know why, but it's probably just that she can't come over the weekend.::
5544::$$$message_0049_0004_0000$$$::"Got it. I'll go to the dojo if I need anything."[lr]::
5545::$$$message_0049_0004_0001$$$::"Yes. That would be great."[lr]::
5546::$$$message_0049_0004_0002$$$::Sakura sighs in relief.[lr]::
5547::$$$message_0049_0004_0003$$$::But the moment Sakura lowers her gaze, her expression stiffens.::
5548::$$$message_0049_0005_0000$$$::"Senpai, your hand."[lr]::
5549::$$$message_0049_0005_0001$$$::"Hm?"[lr]::
5550::$$$message_0049_0005_0002$$$::Sakura is staring at my left hand.[lr]::
5551::$$$message_0049_0005_0003$$$::I look down and see blood trickling from it.::
5552::$$$message_0049_0006_0000$$$::"Huh?"[lr]::
5553::$$$message_0049_0006_0001$$$::I pull up my shirt sleeve.[lr]::
5554::$$$message_0049_0006_0002$$$::Yep. Blood.::
5555::$$$message_0049_0007_0000$$$::"The hell? Did I cut myself with something last night?"[lr]::
5556::$$$message_0049_0007_0001$$$::But I don't feel any pain.[lr]::
5557::$$$message_0049_0007_0002$$$::It looks like there's a welt on my hand...[lr]::
5558::$$$message_0049_0007_0003$$$::The bruise stretches all the way from my shoulder to the back of my hand. It looks like a snake that's trying to reach my palm from the top of my shoulder.::
5559::$$$message_0049_0008_0000$$$::"Well, it doesn't hurt. I'm sure it'll go away soon. I don't think it's anything to worry about."[lr]::
5560::$$$message_0049_0008_0001$$$::"Okay. If you're sure, I won't worry."[lr]::
5561::$$$message_0049_0008_0002$$$::The sight of the blood probably made Sakura sick, since she's keeping her head down.ş